    private static final String STRAT_MEANING = "<p>Word problems on percentages usually hide a simple \u2018part out of whole\u2019 question. Use this routine:</p>" + Doc.steps("<strong>Spot the whole.</strong> Find the total the percent is measured against (marks out of, students out of, etc.).", "<strong>Spot the part.</strong> Identify the smaller amount being compared to the whole.", "<strong>Divide and \u00d7100.</strong> Percent = (part \u00f7 whole) \u00d7 100.", "<strong>Sense-check.</strong> A part smaller than the whole must give under 100%.") + Doc.tip("Watch for the word <em>\u2018NOT\u2019</em>: if 15% are red, then 85% are not red. Subtract from 100%.");
